msgid ""
"This glass jar, 3 inches in diameter, contains 1d4 + 1 doses of a thick "
"mixture that smells faintly of aloe. The jar and its contents weigh 1/2 "
"pound.    \n"
"As an action, one dose of the ointment can be swallowed or applied to the "
"skin. The creature that receives it regains 2d8 + 2 hit points, ceases to be "
"poisoned, and is cured of any disease. \n"
